{"id":522173,"date":[{"year":1972,"month":10,"day":8}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"风雷激","column":"","genre":"","count":"150","ytitle":"","mtitle":"钢厂小景","ftitle":"","authors":["董沛源"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"董沛源"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炼钢工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手持银锹猛一撒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁山半座炉里化；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢钎飞舞画蓝图，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十里钢城金瀑下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电焊工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"焊枪喷吐金银花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"焊工胸中一幅画；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面罩一掀豪情飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喝令高炉平地架。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吊车工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白云深处把营扎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双手牵来方里霞；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吊钩任凭她调遣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁柱钢梁送天下!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起重工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄鏖战阳光下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"食风餐露那算啥；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敢将银丝缚昆仑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"定教山河重安家!"}]}